{"tid":1329255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分析] 如何實現五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-18T07:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:15:15.000Z","uid":265268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15e998e36fa88e04a177baf3d716ac262f06f18b","tid":1329255,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:03:19.000Z","msg":"五大訴求, 歸根究底, 主動解決方法有:<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回送中 ⇨ 普選立法會解決 (新立法會反映民意, 否決惡法)<br />\n2. 撤控義士 ⇨ 法律解決 (要錢, 要人證物證)<br />\n3. 撤暴定性 ⇨ 法律解決 (無視政府定性, 如律政司告以暴動罪: 同上)<br />\n4. 徹查真相 ⇨ 普選特首解決 (新特首應採納民意, 根據《調查委員會條例》成立)<br />\n5. 林鄭下台 ⇨ 普選特首解決<br />\n<br />\n仲有更深層次問題:<br />\n6. 政府官治失效, 立法會失效 ⇨ 普選特首+立法會解決 (短期嘗試光復行動)<br />\n<br />\n所以要滿足五大訴求, 解決深層次矛盾, 除咗等政府突然良心發現之外, 最重要係...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 有錢有證據打官司<br />\n2. 爭取雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">打官司</span>方面, 請各位<span style=\"color: red;\">出錢資助612基金, 立場, 蘋果等, 及保護記者</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">雙普選</span>方面, 有幾個可行方向:<br />\n- 促成美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》, 劍指2020普選立法會<br />\n- 促成英國判定中方違反《中英聯合聲明》, 及作出實質行動<br />\n- 政治升級, 例如籌組臨時立法會(有先例可循), 引發討論, 爭取國際社會支持<br />\n所以, 請<span style=\"color: red;\">支持攬炒巴等團隊有關美國/英國行動, 及為政治升級作初步試探/宣傳</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落, 全民救義士, 籌旗搜證打官司!<br />\n還政於民, 誓要雙普選, 籌組臨時立法會!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2574a2ff719e7275daafb71b11ef439c22f6f0","tid":1329255,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:05:01.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">721見</code></pre><br />\n唔好意思阻一阻你<br />\n鑒於太多人搞錯物資手勢要再宣傳下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再搞錯<strong>索帶</strong>同<strong>長遮</strong>手勢</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oz18Aaq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foz18Aaq.png&h=357e25fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4756197d0b3da432d108c4526357a5395abe066","tid":1329255,"uid":58307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"7.21見<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、設立獨立調查委員會 並徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n四、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n五、立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"688f7046dd088cb8e711b46d363d934f9ee2a501","tid":1329255,"uid":265268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"當然 7.21 要繼續五大訴求!<br />\n<br />\n但我哋要開始諗吓, 當政府講明不再回應時, 我哋要點樣主動 fight for (not just ask for) what we deserve!"},{"pid":"0380c086333d577d245db9b770036efed6332fbe","tid":1329255,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAysjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=3719e578\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n 一、正式撤回修例<br />\n 二、取消暴動定性<br />\n 三、撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n 四、成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 五、立即實行真正雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thre